WEBVTT

01:29.900 --> 01:34.990
[REBIRTH]

01:35.420 --> 01:37.970
[Episode 40]

02:11.030 --> 02:12.360
Charge!

02:12.360 --> 02:15.840
Charge!

02:18.590 --> 02:19.590
Charge!

02:21.560 --> 02:24.870
Charge!

03:47.470 --> 03:48.240
Miaomiao!

03:50.120 --> 03:51.310
Help!

03:51.310 --> 03:52.170
Fang Miaomiao!

03:52.280 --> 03:53.140
Fang Miaomiao!

03:53.360 --> 03:54.470
Help!

03:56.120 --> 03:56.720
Miaomiao!

03:57.800 --> 03:58.910
Fang Miaomiao!

04:01.310 --> 04:03.710
Am I... dying?

04:05.960 --> 04:06.560
Miaomiao!

04:06.800 --> 04:07.400
Miaomiao!

04:08.480 --> 04:09.380
Xiao Ran...

04:09.840 --> 04:10.630
I'm here.

04:13.840 --> 04:15.000
Wang Shi'er...

04:18.390 --> 04:19.390
Lin Mu...

04:19.510 --> 04:20.240
I'm here.

04:23.120 --> 04:25.510
I'm not playing with you anymore.

04:30.070 --> 04:30.920
Miaomiao!

04:31.240 --> 04:32.190
Fang Miaomiao!

04:32.920 --> 04:34.240
No!

04:34.920 --> 04:35.920
Miaomiao!

06:23.920 --> 06:24.800
Huan Huan...

07:42.430 --> 07:43.360
In our next life,

07:44.430 --> 07:45.830
let's be brothers again.

07:46.920 --> 07:47.920
A promise...

07:50.950 --> 07:52.000
is a promise.

09:42.320 --> 09:42.910
Xing.

09:48.630 --> 09:49.510
I'm here.

09:56.670 --> 09:58.880
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

09:57.600 --> 09:58.790
Zhuge Yue...

09:59.000 --> 10:01.540
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

10:01.980 --> 10:03.280
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

10:03.300 --> 10:04.760
♪ My longing surges ♪

10:04.790 --> 10:07.300
♪ I become haggard ♪

10:06.120 --> 10:06.750
Xing.

10:07.910 --> 10:10.350
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

10:10.390 --> 10:13.210
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

10:13.230 --> 10:14.940
♪ My love remains ♪

10:14.000 --> 10:15.120
Zhuge Yue...

10:15.240 --> 10:18.620
♪ But you're already gone ♪

10:17.910 --> 10:19.790
you finally came to pick me up.

10:18.640 --> 10:20.910
♪ What I seek in life ♪

10:20.940 --> 10:22.520
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

10:22.550 --> 10:25.130
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

10:22.630 --> 10:23.870
I'm late.

10:25.150 --> 10:26.740
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

10:26.760 --> 10:29.950
♪ My longing still rests ♪

10:29.980 --> 10:32.340
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

10:32.360 --> 10:33.870
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

10:33.900 --> 10:36.550
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

10:36.580 --> 10:41.440
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

10:38.270 --> 10:38.870
Xing?

10:41.460 --> 10:42.860
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

10:41.670 --> 10:42.360
Xing?

10:42.880 --> 10:45.130
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

10:43.440 --> 10:44.240
Xing!

10:45.150 --> 10:47.600
♪ How do we start over? ♪

10:47.620 --> 10:50.940
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

10:50.960 --> 10:53.220
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

10:53.240 --> 10:56.650
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

10:53.960 --> 10:56.480
Xing!

10:56.670 --> 10:58.990
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

10:59.010 --> 11:01.900
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

11:01.920 --> 11:06.460
♪ In the end ♪

11:04.320 --> 11:05.510
Xing...

11:08.040 --> 11:11.670
♪ It can only be praised ♪

11:30.120 --> 11:31.670
Wait for me!

11:32.630 --> 11:33.160
Hurry up!

11:34.550 --> 11:35.390
Come on!

11:40.240 --> 11:40.840
Stop.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.900
Chu's Mansion, Leping Alley?

11:58.080 --> 11:58.910
Thank you.

11:59.200 --> 11:59.870
Take care.

12:02.790 --> 12:04.240
You two look sneaky

12:04.240 --> 12:05.170
and suspicious.

12:05.550 --> 12:08.360
You don't look familiar.

12:08.670 --> 12:10.270
You're not from here, right?

12:12.270 --> 12:13.360
We are

12:15.510 --> 12:16.970
merchants from Great Yan.

12:17.240 --> 12:18.630
We are looking for Leping Alley.

12:18.630 --> 12:19.390
Little boy,

12:19.790 --> 12:21.520
do you know where this place is?

12:21.550 --> 12:23.200
I won't lead the way for sneaky

12:23.200 --> 12:24.630
and suspicious people.

12:27.150 --> 12:29.030
I will take you to Leping Alley.

12:29.630 --> 12:31.200
Why are you helping the bad guys?

12:31.200 --> 12:31.960
Brother,

12:31.960 --> 12:32.960
Mom has always taught us

12:32.960 --> 12:34.910
since childhood to stand up for justice

12:34.910 --> 12:36.080
and help others,

12:36.480 --> 12:39.600
especially good-looking men and women.

12:39.790 --> 12:40.510
Dad said

12:40.510 --> 12:41.870
there's no use in looking good.

12:41.870 --> 12:43.150
We should be like him and Mom,

12:43.150 --> 12:44.630
good-looking and good at martial arts.

12:44.630 --> 12:46.030
They are our role models.

12:47.870 --> 12:49.270
Little boy, little girl,

12:49.360 --> 12:50.750
you are also very beautiful.

12:50.750 --> 12:52.790
You are the best-looking kids
I've ever seen.

12:52.790 --> 12:53.480
Really?

12:54.240 --> 12:54.910
Yes.

12:56.910 --> 12:58.440
More good-looking than me.

12:58.630 --> 13:00.270
Finally, someone praised my brother!

13:00.270 --> 13:02.000
Finally!

13:02.550 --> 13:04.300
Since you are honest,

13:04.330 --> 13:05.060
come with me.

13:05.320 --> 13:06.960
Shadow puppet show!

13:08.110 --> 13:10.570
-Time for the shadow puppet show!
-Let's go!

13:11.460 --> 13:12.740
It's starting!

13:12.870 --> 13:15.600
Come and watch
the shadow puppet show, everyone!

13:16.750 --> 13:17.880
Good-looking kids,

13:18.240 --> 13:20.510
why did you bring us
to a shadow puppet show?

13:20.510 --> 13:21.550
This is the most popular shadow play

13:21.550 --> 13:22.840
in Ximengcheng.

13:22.840 --> 13:24.440
Everyone who comes for the first time
has to watch it.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.960
You get to see it
right after entering the city.

13:25.960 --> 13:27.200
You are so lucky.

13:27.200 --> 13:29.400
It is said that the current Ximengcheng

13:29.450 --> 13:31.980
was built by King Ximeng
and General Chu Qiao.

13:32.350 --> 13:35.470
General Chu Qiao not only fought
side by side

13:35.500 --> 13:37.910
with Yan Xun, the King of Great Yan,

13:38.600 --> 13:42.030
but was also a confidant
of the late Emperor of Biantang.

13:42.840 --> 13:45.440
What a remarkable woman.

13:45.800 --> 13:46.980
Truly a remarkable person.

13:46.980 --> 13:49.630
At that time, the people of Great Yong
hadn't awakened,

13:49.630 --> 13:51.960
still living in the shackles of slavery.

13:52.270 --> 13:54.790
Great Yong was dissatisfied
with Ximeng's independence,

13:54.790 --> 13:57.440
so they sent an army to attack Ximeng.

14:00.030 --> 14:03.720
General Chu Qiao led the army
to fight against the Yong Army.

14:03.720 --> 14:06.080
In the final battle with Great Yong,

14:06.240 --> 14:07.440
General Chu Qiao

14:07.440 --> 14:09.750
and Zhuge Yue, who was then
the military counselor of Great Yong,

14:09.750 --> 14:11.120
cooperated from inside and outside

14:11.120 --> 14:14.270
and finally won the war.

14:14.840 --> 14:17.240
Bravo!

14:17.840 --> 14:19.990
Although the shadow puppet show
presents it in a simplified way,

14:19.990 --> 14:21.910
back then they really worked together

14:21.910 --> 14:22.670
and almost died.

14:22.670 --> 14:25.130
Even General Chu
thought Zhuge Yue was dead.

14:25.200 --> 14:28.080
Your storytelling is better
than the shadow puppet show.

14:28.080 --> 14:28.870
Since then,

14:29.080 --> 14:31.670
Great Yong has no longer
been as strong as before.

14:31.670 --> 14:34.390
However, a foreign tribe, Quanrong,
took advantage of the situation

14:34.390 --> 14:36.150
and attacked the Central Plains.

14:36.150 --> 14:37.790
General Chu took the lead,

14:37.910 --> 14:39.870
uniting the forces of Ximeng, Great Yan,

14:39.870 --> 14:42.320
Biantang, and Great Yong,

14:42.320 --> 14:45.320
and finally defeated the Quanrong
completely!

14:45.320 --> 14:46.390
Bravo!

14:46.720 --> 14:48.080
Bravo! Bravo!

14:48.390 --> 14:51.390
However, in this battle,

14:51.720 --> 14:53.510
General Chu was severely injured

14:53.510 --> 14:54.910
and almost died.

14:55.550 --> 14:57.840
She fell on the battlefield,

14:58.360 --> 15:02.030
with only the common people in her heart.

15:03.790 --> 15:04.630
Sir,

15:04.630 --> 15:05.390
don't worry.

15:05.550 --> 15:07.210
General Chu is alive and well.

15:07.270 --> 15:09.320
Although she was severely injured
on the battlefield,

15:09.320 --> 15:10.850
Zhuge Yue brought her back

15:10.870 --> 15:12.360
from amidst thousands of troops

15:12.360 --> 15:16.420
and saved her with the miraculous medicine
of the divine doctor Xiao Ran.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.150
Pretty boy,

15:21.270 --> 15:22.630
how do you know this?

15:23.270 --> 15:25.070
Zhuge Yunzhou, Zhuge Yunsheng!

15:25.790 --> 15:26.600
Father!

15:26.960 --> 15:27.720
Father!

15:29.080 --> 15:30.080
-Father!
-Hurry!

15:30.240 --> 15:32.640
If you don't go home now,
you'll be spanked!

15:33.000 --> 15:33.750
Spanked!

15:39.720 --> 15:41.780
Tell me, what game did you play today?

15:57.600 --> 15:58.400
Open the door.

15:58.480 --> 16:00.120
Okay. Be quiet.

16:00.600 --> 16:02.400
Don't let your mother notice us.

16:02.480 --> 16:04.680
You finally remembered you have a home?

16:06.390 --> 16:07.270
Naughty.

16:21.960 --> 16:24.000
Pretty sir.

16:25.840 --> 16:26.480
Yan Xun.

16:36.080 --> 16:37.320
You two came just in time.

16:37.320 --> 16:38.320
We are busy.

16:38.320 --> 16:38.910
Come and help.

16:38.910 --> 16:39.550
Join us.

16:44.440 --> 16:45.150
Meat!

16:45.920 --> 16:47.650
-Time for meat!
-Time for meat!

17:10.150 --> 17:11.800
[36 years later]

17:31.000 --> 17:31.750
Chu!

17:36.350 --> 17:37.150
Your Majesty?

17:39.680 --> 17:40.480
Your Majesty!

17:41.240 --> 17:42.040
Your Majesty!

17:49.000 --> 17:51.070
Did you dream of General Xiuli again?

18:00.270 --> 18:01.960
Where is Queen Helian?

18:05.960 --> 18:07.400
Be careful, Your Majesty.

18:07.400 --> 18:08.730
You are confused again.

18:15.640 --> 18:18.400
Queen Helian has been gone for 10 years.

18:23.000 --> 18:24.350
Ten years?

18:25.240 --> 18:26.640
If you miss her,

18:26.830 --> 18:28.160
you can visit the imperial tomb

18:28.160 --> 18:30.420
after we return from the hunting ground.

18:37.510 --> 18:38.750
Is someone

18:39.510 --> 18:41.030
waiting outside the tent?

18:41.270 --> 18:42.720
It is General Helian Tu.

18:43.200 --> 18:44.510
She said Emperor Changzhao of Biantang

18:44.510 --> 18:46.590
has sent a new diplomatic letter
of goodwill

18:46.590 --> 18:48.920
and wants to discuss this matter with you.

18:49.800 --> 18:54.120
Emperor Changzhao... Li Xiuyi...

18:57.000 --> 18:59.400
How long has it been
since Li Ce passed away?

18:59.440 --> 19:00.240
Your Majesty,

19:00.830 --> 19:04.030
the late Emperor of Biantang
passed away 46 years ago.

19:08.240 --> 19:10.310
Forty-six years?

19:13.880 --> 19:15.640
I'm old too.

19:32.860 --> 19:36.830
[Helian Tu, Helian Tribe]

19:35.270 --> 19:36.750
Greetings, Your Majesty.

19:37.200 --> 19:38.000
Speak.

19:40.960 --> 19:41.880
Your Majesty,

19:42.640 --> 19:44.480
according to the five-year tradition,

19:44.480 --> 19:46.400
the Emperor of Biantang
has sent a diplomatic letter.

19:46.400 --> 19:47.480
Based on previous treaties,

19:47.480 --> 19:49.480
they added a new trade policy

19:49.480 --> 19:51.210
and stated that if you approve,

19:51.240 --> 19:53.100
they are willing to send 30 envoys

19:53.100 --> 19:54.640
to come to the Capital of Great Yan
with gifts

19:54.640 --> 19:57.440
and establish friendly relations
with Great Yan.

19:57.720 --> 19:58.590
Got it.

19:59.070 --> 19:59.550
Also,

20:00.110 --> 20:01.270
our northeastern border

20:01.270 --> 20:02.510
was repeatedly harassed

20:02.510 --> 20:03.880
by Quanrong people last month.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.440
Fortunately, there were not many of them.

20:05.440 --> 20:07.680
They only burned, killed, and looted
in border villages,

20:07.680 --> 20:08.960
without launching a further invasion.

20:08.960 --> 20:10.480
I sent people to ambush nearby,

20:10.480 --> 20:11.640
attacked their troops,

20:11.640 --> 20:13.200
and found out they were just
a band of robbers

20:13.200 --> 20:15.550
roaming between Great Yan and Ximeng.

20:16.070 --> 20:18.110
Because it's extremely cold this year,

20:18.110 --> 20:20.030
it's hard to survive
in Quanrong's territory.

20:20.030 --> 20:20.960
What about

20:22.000 --> 20:22.920
Ximeng?

20:24.350 --> 20:25.160
Ximeng?

20:28.400 --> 20:30.160
Is Ximeng alright?

20:31.270 --> 20:32.030
Are they...

20:33.110 --> 20:34.400
still alive?

20:35.830 --> 20:36.630
Your Majesty,

20:36.830 --> 20:39.200
the canal connecting Ximeng
to our territory is being built,

20:39.200 --> 20:41.160
and ships will be able
to pass through next year.

20:41.160 --> 20:43.590
Last month, King Ximeng introduced
the official lending policy,

20:43.590 --> 20:44.720
the border trade policy,

20:44.720 --> 20:46.440
and the market arbitration regulations.

20:46.440 --> 20:47.900
He also issued a new decree

20:48.270 --> 20:51.240
saying there will be a day
for suggestions every month.

20:51.240 --> 20:52.000
Xi...

20:55.400 --> 20:56.680
All of you, go back.

20:58.270 --> 20:59.110
I am tired.

21:01.550 --> 21:02.790
Yes.

21:22.000 --> 21:26.170
[To Zhuge Yue]

21:31.750 --> 21:32.810
I'm not convinced.

21:33.030 --> 21:34.310
I'm not trying to pick fights,

21:34.310 --> 21:36.510
but King Ximeng,
though you don't call yourself a king,

21:36.510 --> 21:37.440
you're still

21:37.440 --> 21:38.770
a high and mighty noble.

21:39.680 --> 21:40.310
How could you understand

21:40.310 --> 21:42.240
the real lives of ordinary people?

21:42.480 --> 21:44.210
You asked me to pay him 45 coins.

21:44.550 --> 21:46.240
Then what about my losses?

21:47.070 --> 21:48.590
What losses do you have?

21:48.750 --> 21:49.880
Your chickens

21:49.880 --> 21:51.790
damaged my barley field.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.000
With so many chickens,

21:53.000 --> 21:54.680
I only estimated the loss at one acre.

21:54.680 --> 21:55.880
That's already less than it should be.

21:55.880 --> 21:57.310
If my own land

21:57.310 --> 21:58.440
hadn't been requisitioned
to build the road,

21:58.440 --> 22:00.350
I wouldn't have moved next to you.

22:00.680 --> 22:01.640
And my chickens

22:02.000 --> 22:04.350
wouldn't have gotten into your field
and eaten your barley.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.830
That has nothing to do with me.

22:05.830 --> 22:07.030
-Alright.
-Wasn't it your...

22:07.030 --> 22:08.490
You don't know yet, do you?

22:08.750 --> 22:11.510
According to the new border trade policy
enacted this year,

22:11.510 --> 22:13.880
for any land requisitioned for the road,

22:14.550 --> 22:16.880
the owners are entitled to compensation.

22:17.880 --> 22:20.880
There's such a good thing?
Giving away money for free?

22:21.790 --> 22:24.960
This money
didn't just appear out of thin air.

22:25.070 --> 22:26.670
Ximeng is building this road

22:26.750 --> 22:29.440
to make trade with Biantang
more convenient.

22:29.830 --> 22:31.480
This will allow
seasonal sea buckthorn berries

22:31.480 --> 22:33.680
to be transported
to Biantang more quickly.

22:33.680 --> 22:35.340
The profit from these berries

22:35.830 --> 22:37.760
is the source of the compensation.

22:39.270 --> 22:40.720
Take them to collect the compensation.

22:40.720 --> 22:41.270
Yes.

22:42.030 --> 22:42.960
Make way!

22:43.240 --> 22:44.640
Someone wants to make me a slave!

22:44.640 --> 22:45.160
Make way!

22:45.160 --> 22:45.720
Stop!

22:46.750 --> 22:47.200
Stop running!

22:47.200 --> 22:48.000
Make way!

22:48.000 --> 22:49.030
-Stop!
-King Ximeng!

22:49.030 --> 22:50.110
King Ximeng, save me!

22:50.110 --> 22:51.310
King Ximeng, save me!

22:51.830 --> 22:53.490
Someone wants me to be a slave!

22:53.580 --> 22:54.300
Get up.

22:56.400 --> 22:59.070
Ximeng abolished slavery many years ago.

22:59.350 --> 23:00.440
According to the law,

23:00.440 --> 23:02.510
secretly trading slaves is a felony.

23:04.590 --> 23:06.830
Who dares to take her to be a slave?

23:07.160 --> 23:08.510
King Ximeng, please judge fairly!

23:08.510 --> 23:10.420
Our Young Master is marrying her
by a betrothal contract.

23:10.420 --> 23:12.240
It's a proper arranged marriage!

23:12.240 --> 23:13.570
It's not slave trading!

23:13.790 --> 23:15.270
You bribed my father
with the betrothal gifts.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.200
That's why he agreed.

23:16.200 --> 23:17.920
You never asked for my opinion.

23:17.920 --> 23:19.830
How is that any different
from slave trading?

23:19.830 --> 23:21.110
Your father accepted the betrothal gifts,

23:21.110 --> 23:22.830
so you are now betrothed
to our Young Master.

23:22.830 --> 23:24.630
Complaining here is pointless.

23:24.700 --> 23:25.260
You...

23:25.830 --> 23:27.550
Yun Chuqiao?

23:29.270 --> 23:32.110
Your name is Chuqiao?

23:32.430 --> 23:34.000
Yes. Can't it be?

23:34.510 --> 23:36.200
My dream is to become a female general

23:36.200 --> 23:37.510
just like her.

23:37.790 --> 23:39.790
That's why I changed my name to this.

23:39.880 --> 23:42.000
So you escaped your arranged marriage

23:42.000 --> 23:43.880
because you want to be a female general?

23:43.880 --> 23:44.440
Yes.

23:44.960 --> 23:47.090
I'm going to enlist in the Ximeng Army.

23:57.470 --> 24:00.160
The battlefield is not a playground.

24:07.270 --> 24:08.870
You've got decent reflexes.

24:11.510 --> 24:13.640
But you still lack training.

24:14.200 --> 24:15.530
You caught me off guard.

24:15.640 --> 24:17.350
If you dare, try me again.

24:29.480 --> 24:31.480
Take this and find General Chu.

24:32.200 --> 24:34.120
She'll let you join the Ximeng Army.

24:34.120 --> 24:36.520
If you're capable of becoming a centurion,

24:36.790 --> 24:39.350
you'll earn 150 coins in monthly pay.

24:39.640 --> 24:40.770
In less than 2 years,

24:41.150 --> 24:45.210
you'll earn enough to pay back
the betrothal money your father accepted.

24:46.270 --> 24:47.110
See this?

24:47.310 --> 24:49.000
This is the official approval
from King Ximeng.

24:49.000 --> 24:50.730
I'm part of the Ximeng Army now.

24:51.110 --> 24:52.550
The money my father took from you,

24:52.550 --> 24:54.210
I will definitely pay it back.

24:55.480 --> 24:56.240
Thank you.

25:08.390 --> 25:13.050
[To Zhuge Yue]

25:46.110 --> 25:47.720
It's already March.

25:48.590 --> 25:49.920
Why is it still snowing?

25:50.680 --> 25:52.740
It's always like this in Mount Ximin.

25:52.960 --> 25:54.200
But in about a month and a half,

25:54.200 --> 25:55.600
the weather will warm up.

25:55.830 --> 25:57.830
When the snow on the mountains melts

25:57.830 --> 25:59.480
and the water of Ximin Lake
flows over here,

25:59.480 --> 26:00.610
spring will arrive.

26:01.030 --> 26:02.110
The grasslands in Great Yan

26:02.110 --> 26:03.400
will surely flourish again—

26:03.400 --> 26:05.860
it'll be another good year
for the herdsmen.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.000
Your Majesty!

28:17.550 --> 28:18.270
Zhuge Yue,

28:19.680 --> 28:21.590
I miss Great Yan's hot pot.

28:50.240 --> 28:51.350
Am I late?

28:52.000 --> 28:53.200
You came just in time.

28:53.310 --> 28:54.840
The hot pot is just boiling.

29:25.480 --> 29:26.070
Li Ce,

29:27.440 --> 29:29.480
have you ever truly loved someone?

29:33.510 --> 29:34.240
Your Highness!

29:34.240 --> 29:35.350
Your Highness!

29:37.270 --> 29:39.280
There is no absolute beauty in history;

29:39.280 --> 29:41.740
one pleasing to the eye
is a beautiful woman.

29:42.920 --> 29:43.750
Qiao.

29:45.790 --> 29:46.960
I like you.

29:51.680 --> 29:52.640
Your Majesty, are you here again

29:52.640 --> 29:54.050
waiting for General Xiuli?

29:54.050 --> 29:56.250
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

29:56.370 --> 29:58.910
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

29:59.350 --> 30:00.650
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

30:00.670 --> 30:02.140
♪ My longing surges ♪

30:02.160 --> 30:04.670
♪ I become haggard ♪

30:02.790 --> 30:03.550
Qiao!

30:04.240 --> 30:04.960
Qiao!

30:05.280 --> 30:07.720
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

30:05.920 --> 30:07.520
Qiao comes back triumphant!

30:07.760 --> 30:10.580
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

30:08.070 --> 30:09.070
Qiao!

30:10.610 --> 30:12.310
♪ My love remains ♪

30:12.620 --> 30:15.990
♪ But you're already gone ♪

30:14.200 --> 30:16.550
Then can you temporarily
treat me as that person,

30:16.010 --> 30:18.290
♪ What I seek in life ♪

30:17.070 --> 30:18.550
until you truly forget him

30:18.310 --> 30:19.890
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

30:19.110 --> 30:20.000
and are no longer in pain?

30:19.920 --> 30:22.500
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

30:20.480 --> 30:22.400
If you don't want to get married yet,

30:22.400 --> 30:24.070
we can pretend
today's wedding never happened.

30:22.530 --> 30:24.110
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

30:24.140 --> 30:27.320
♪ My longing still rests ♪

30:24.590 --> 30:26.050
I can keep waiting for you,

30:27.110 --> 30:28.830
until you fall in love with me,

30:27.350 --> 30:29.710
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

30:29.590 --> 30:31.830
until the day
you truly want to be my wife.

30:29.730 --> 30:31.250
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

30:31.270 --> 30:33.930
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

30:33.950 --> 30:38.810
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

30:38.830 --> 30:40.230
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

30:40.250 --> 30:42.500
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

30:42.530 --> 30:44.970
♪ How do we start over? ♪

30:45.000 --> 30:48.310
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

30:48.330 --> 30:50.590
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

30:50.610 --> 30:54.020
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

30:51.960 --> 30:53.760
You are going to be a mother soon.

30:54.050 --> 30:56.360
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

30:54.400 --> 30:56.200
How can you still be so careless?

30:56.390 --> 30:59.270
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

30:57.790 --> 30:59.640
It will soon be the first festival

30:59.290 --> 31:03.830
♪ In the end ♪

31:00.000 --> 31:01.590
for our family of three.

31:02.200 --> 31:04.000
I am no longer alone.

31:06.830 --> 31:08.030
I am so happy.

31:16.820 --> 31:19.020
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

31:19.140 --> 31:21.680
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

31:22.120 --> 31:23.420
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

31:23.440 --> 31:24.910
♪ My longing surges ♪

31:24.920 --> 31:27.640
I want to live a life
that truly belongs to me,

31:24.930 --> 31:27.440
♪ I become haggard ♪

31:28.050 --> 31:30.490
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

31:28.160 --> 31:30.160
finding a place where no one knows me

31:30.200 --> 31:32.640
and living peacefully and freely.

31:30.530 --> 31:33.350
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

31:33.380 --> 31:35.080
♪ My love remains ♪

31:34.640 --> 31:35.590
What about you?

31:35.390 --> 31:38.760
♪ But you're already gone ♪

31:37.000 --> 31:38.260
Let's go to Yunzhou...

31:38.780 --> 31:41.060
♪ What I seek in life ♪

31:40.310 --> 31:42.070
or anywhere you want to go,

31:41.080 --> 31:42.660
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

31:42.690 --> 31:45.270
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

31:42.720 --> 31:44.780
and live a life with just the two of us.

31:45.300 --> 31:46.880
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

31:46.910 --> 31:50.090
♪ My longing still rests ♪

31:50.120 --> 31:52.480
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

31:52.500 --> 31:54.020
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

31:53.640 --> 31:54.440
Helian!

31:54.040 --> 31:56.700
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

31:56.720 --> 32:01.580
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

32:01.600 --> 32:03.000
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

32:03.020 --> 32:05.270
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

32:05.070 --> 32:07.920
A woman should look like a woman.

32:05.300 --> 32:07.740
♪ How do we start over? ♪

32:07.770 --> 32:11.080
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

32:11.100 --> 32:13.360
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

32:11.440 --> 32:12.970
I want to borrow your horse.

32:13.380 --> 32:16.790
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

32:13.880 --> 32:16.230
Why does everyone
want to borrow a horse from me?

32:16.230 --> 32:18.000
My horse has already been borrowed.

32:16.820 --> 32:19.130
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

32:18.680 --> 32:21.510
Now all I have left
is this donkey used for milling.

32:19.160 --> 32:22.040
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

32:21.790 --> 32:22.440
Zhao Che.

32:22.060 --> 32:26.600
♪ In the end ♪

32:23.960 --> 32:25.110
Let go of all this

32:26.550 --> 32:27.550
and leave with me.

32:27.810 --> 32:28.800
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

32:28.860 --> 32:31.110
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

32:29.030 --> 32:29.640
Okay.

32:30.480 --> 32:31.720
Let's leave together.

32:31.130 --> 32:33.410
♪ How do we start over? ♪

32:33.520 --> 32:36.830
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

32:36.850 --> 32:39.110
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

32:39.130 --> 32:42.540
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

32:42.570 --> 32:44.880
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

32:44.910 --> 32:47.790
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

32:47.810 --> 32:52.350
♪ In the end ♪

32:53.890 --> 32:59.270
♪ It can only be praised ♪

33:08.060 --> 33:11.920
[Qingshan Manor]

33:20.350 --> 33:21.210
Brother Shiyi.

33:23.310 --> 33:24.710
We have finally retired.

33:26.030 --> 33:27.790
Where do you plan to go?

33:34.030 --> 33:35.160
The world is so vast!

33:35.590 --> 33:36.590
Anywhere is fine!

33:51.820 --> 33:54.730
♪ We mock karma ♪

33:55.660 --> 33:58.240
♪ For being unfair ♪

33:58.660 --> 34:00.640
♪ Why is life ♪

34:00.890 --> 34:04.940
♪ Often filled with regrets? ♪

34:06.590 --> 34:09.020
♪ The snow falls ♪

34:09.460 --> 34:12.630
♪ With fate ♪

34:13.570 --> 34:14.810
♪ It will eventually ♪

34:15.260 --> 34:17.260
♪ Fall before ♪

34:17.290 --> 34:19.750
♪ The dawn ♪

34:20.219 --> 34:22.429
♪ As a foreigner ♪

34:22.610 --> 34:27.150
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

34:27.440 --> 34:29.710
♪ Wander ♪

34:29.929 --> 34:34.139
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

34:34.639 --> 34:36.739
♪ Traveling alone ♪

34:37.040 --> 34:39.040
♪ In a world ♪

34:39.060 --> 34:42.620
♪ Where fate is unkind ♪

34:42.650 --> 34:43.820
♪ Look ♪

34:44.219 --> 34:48.429
♪ The mortal world has forgotten me ♪

34:51.110 --> 34:52.659
♪ I wish ♪

34:53.050 --> 35:00.010
♪ You'll forget me ♪
